---
layout: base.njk
title: Field Guide
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<div class="page-header">
  <h2>Field Guide to Tennessee Cryptids</h2>
  <p>A comprehensive index of unclassified creatures reported across the state. Entries are compiled from eyewitness accounts, local records, and field investigations conducted by TCRN researchers.</p>
</div>

<hr class="section-divider">

<div class="cryptid-grid">
  {% for cryptid in collections.cryptids %}
  <div class="cryptid-card">
    {% if cryptid.data.image %}
    <div class="card-image">
      <img src="{{ cryptid.data.image }}" alt="{{ cryptid.data.title }}">
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="card-image card-image--placeholder">
      <span class="placeholder-glyph">?</span>
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="card-body">
      <h3 class="card-title"><a href="{{ cryptid.url }}">{{ cryptid.data.title }}</a></h3>
      {% if cryptid.data.region %}
      <div class="card-region">{{ cryptid.data.region }}</div>
      {% endif %}
      {% if cryptid.data.summary %}
      <p class="card-summary">{{ cryptid.data.summary }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="card-tags">
        {% if cryptid.data.status %}
        <span class="tag tag--status">{{ cryptid.data.status }}</span>
        {% endif %}
        {% if cryptid.data.danger %}
        <span class="tag tag--danger">Danger: {{ cryptid.data.danger }}</span>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      <a href="{{ cryptid.url }}" class="card-link">View Entry →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
